OL,4,C'second-class citizen' amid support
OL,5,Cworry
OL,7,FRhondda Cynon Taf Council says it
OL,8,Fcannot comment on individual cases but
OL,9,Fsays it recognises the contribution
OL,10,Fmade by unpaid carers and has provided
OL,11,Fa range of support services for many
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,FDavid said: "Unfortunately nowadays
OL,15,Fwith her being in bed all the time,
OL,16,Fwe're stuck at home, it is quite a
OL,17,Fchallenge.
OL,19,F"I gave up work in 2014 - I worked in
OL,20,FHampton Court Palace as a state
OL,21,Fdepartment warder.
