OL,7,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"We highly value the vital role unpaid
OL,9,Fcarers play in our communities and are
OL,10,Fcommitted to ensuring support
OL,11,Fcontinues to be available.
OL,13,F"Since 2022, we have invested #42
OL,14,Fmillion to deliver support to unpaid
OL,15,Fcarers. This includes a #9 million
OL,16,FShort Breaks Scheme to enable carers
OL,17,Fto have a break from their caring role
OL,18,Fand the Carers Support Fund which has
OL,19,Fhelped more than 24,000 carers access
OL,20,Ffinancial support and services.
